### Solution Overview

AuditGuardX is an AI powered compliance and risk management platform that transforms the way organizagtions review and manage their most important documentation, including contracts, policy manuals, regulatory guidance by instantly flagging non-compliant sections and riskly language. It provides actionalable, plain-engilsh recommendations and guidance on every step to resolve or correct the identified compliance gaps or issues.

### How it works
- User uploads a document (PDF, Word or text)
- User selects a compliance framework (SOC2, HIPPA, GDPR, PCI-DSS, ISO27001, SOX)
- AuditGuardX processes the full document, identifies the violations
- AuditGuardX generagtes details about each identified issues, regulatory references and remediation steps

### Target Users
- Compliance teams
- legal departments
- HR professionals
- Auditors
- business managers
- anyone responsible with document compliance and risk management

### How users interact with the application
- No technical training or previous compliance knowlege required.
- Simply create a policy document for example "Data Retention Policy Manual"
- Choose a compliance frame and run the check on the document to get results in seconds.
- Designg for both technial and non-technical users



### AI Impact
By directly automating tedious manual document reviews to reduces human errors, AuditGuardX enable organizations to rapidly identify, understand and remediate compliance risk before they become a costly problem. It dramatically accelerates compliance workflows, scales to any document size and reduces reliance on external compliance consultant or expensive legal reviews. The solution can be immediately customize or extended to include new regulations, languages and risk types.